%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20at%20least%2C%20they%20did.%20Demand%20for%20flawless%20teeth%20is%20still%20high.%20Getting%20your%20teeth%20shaved%20down%20irreversibly%3F%20Not%20so%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20%26quot%3Bno-prep%20veneers%26quot%3B%20are%20rising%20up%20as%20the%20new%20%26quot%3Bit%26quot%3B%20procedure.%20The%20result%20is%20similar%20to%20traditional%20veneers%2C%20but%20there's%20no%20filing%2C%20drilling%2C%20or%20grinding%20involved%20to%20make%20room%20for%20the%20porcelain%20shells.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20all%20part%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bquiet%20glow-up%26quot%3B%20trend.%20Forget%20Botox%2C%20people%20want%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrotox-review-botox-antiaging-treatment-smoothes-wrinkles-lines-freezing-face-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emicrotox%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Instead%20of%20face%20and%20neck%20lifts%2C%20cosmetic%20surgeons%20are%20fielding%20requests%20for%20biostimulators%20and%20skin%20boosters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProponents%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-bryan-johnsons-2-million-dollar-routine-to-live-100-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBryan%20Johnson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20famed%20longevity%20seeker%2C%20who%20has%20spoken%20about%20his%20decision%20to%20get%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40_bryan_johnson_%2Fvideo%2F7462191695552073003%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno-prep%20veneers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20improve%20the%20whiteness%20of%20his%20teeth%20without%20shaving%20them%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20young%20people%20see%20videos%20of%20people%20sharing%20their%20shaved-down%20teeth%2C%20and%20they%20are%20being%20educated%20about%20the%20high%20risk%26quot%3B%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktokers-share-dental-horrors-from-unlicensed-veneer-techs-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong-term%20damage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dr.%20Lilya%20Horowitz%2C%20cosmetic%20and%20general%20dentist%20and%20owner%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.domino.dental%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Domino%20Dental%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHorowitz%20says%20she%20has%20seen%20an%20uptick%20in%20people%20coming%20into%20her%20Brooklyn%20clinic%20for%20%26quot%3Blow-risk%26quot%3B%20cosmetic%20tweaks%20like%20no-prep%20veneers%20to%20revamp%20broken%2C%20chipped%2C%20cracked%2C%20or%20discolored%20teeth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20you%20know%20about%20the%20risks%20of%20cutting%20your%20teeth%20down%2C%20the%20more%20you%20will%20be%20motivated%20to%20seek%20more%20conservative%20options.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo-prep%20veneers%20are%20not%20for%20everyone.%20People%20with%20larger%20teeth%20or%20more%20severely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-got-laser-teeth-whitening-in-mexico-to-save-money-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscolored%20teeth%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20fare%20better%20with%20traditional%20veneers.%20Plus%2C%20they're%20no%20cheaper%20%E2%80%94%20often%20more%20expensive.%20Still%2C%20in%20this%20era%20of%20subtle%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbotox-injections-fillers-plastic-surgery-gen-z-social-media-filters-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etweakments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20they're%20emerging%20as%20the%20go-to%20job%20in%20cosmetic%20dentistry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ecf9cce3-8561-47de-a838-835f59a88a94%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESkip%20the%20drilling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20traditional%20and%20no-prep%20veneers%20start%20the%20same%20way%3A%20after%20a%20good%20cleaning%20and%20polishing%2C%20your%20dentist%20gets%203D%20scans%20of%20your%20teeth%2C%20dental%20radiographs%2C%20and%20high-res%20photos%20to%20create%20a%20prototype%20of%20your%20veneers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20getting%20no-preps%2C%20the%20prototype