%20dentist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdrjonmarashi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Jon%20Marashi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whose%20clients%20include%20Ryan%20Seacrest%2C%20Kate%20Hudson%2C%20and%20Ben%20Affleck%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr.%20Jon%20Marashi%2C%20a%20cosmetic%20dentist%20to%20the%20stars%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f03491b8b41a9673fcb9a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDr.%20Jon%20Marashi%2C%20a%20cosmetic%20dentist%20to%20the%20stars%2C%20says%20demand%20is%20soaring%20for%20no-prep%20veneers%3Cp%3EAntar%20Hanif%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20veneers%20first%20emerged%2C%20the%20procedure%20was%20less%20invasive%2C%20since%20the%20material%20of%20choice%20%E2%80%94%20feldspathic%20porcelain%20%E2%80%94%20was%20very%20thin%20and%20could%20fit%20neatly%20on%20most%20teeth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20stronger%20materials%20have%20emerged%20that%20are%20better%20at%20covering%20up%20imperfections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20materials%2C%20such%20as%20zirconia%20or%20lithium%20disilicate%2C%20are%20now%20the%20standard.%20They're%20up%20to%2050%25%20thicker%2C%20making%20them%20less%20fragile%20and%20easier%20to%20work%20with%20for%20both%20veneers%20(covering%20the%20front%20of%20the%20tooth)%20and%20crowns%20(wrapping%20around%20the%20whole%20tooth).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20thickness%20also%20requires%20more%20room.%20Dentists%20should%20only%20shave%20off%2C%20at%20most%2C%200.5mm%20per%20tooth%2C%20but%20the%20thick%20material%20can%20cover%20up%20imprecision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20practitioners%20%26quot%3Bexcessively%20drill%20a%20tooth%20down%20to%20a%20tiny%20nub%26quot%3B%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20job%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrmarashi.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarashi%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%20%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20over%20the%20years%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20tendency%20for%20the%20tooth%20to%20be%20excessively%20drilled%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20why%20we're%20seeing%20the%20pendulum%20shift%20toward%20the%20no-drill%20option.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETeeth%20aren't%20like%20hair%20or%20skin%3B%20they%20won't%20just%20grow%20back%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-regrets-failed-veneer-procedure-fake-teeth-falling-off-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20veneers%3C%2Fa%3E%20route%20more%20%26quot%3Bpermanent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20bitter%20pill%20for%20Rebecca%20Bacon%2C%20a%2032-year-old%20speech-language%20pathologist%20who%20got%20traditional%20veneers%20in%202009%2C%20when%20she%20was%2016.%20In%20high%20school%2C%20she%20was%20self-conscious%20about%20two%20of%20her%20teeth%20that%20grew%20smaller%20than%20average.%20Eventually%20her%20parents%20and%20dentist%20agreed%20on%20a%20solution%3A%20her%20teeth%20were%20shaved%20down%20and%20covered%20with%20perfect%20porcelain%20shells.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20while%2C%20her%20new%20pearly%20whites%20were%20excellent.%20But%20cracks%20started%20to%20show%20%E2%80%94%20literally%20%E2%80%94%20no%20matter%20how%20carefully%20she%20chewed%20her%20food.%20%26quot%3BMy%20veneers%20aren't%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20Bacon%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BOne%20has%20slipped%20and%20shows%20a%20sliver%20of%20tooth%20at%20the%20top%20and%20the%20other%20cracked%20and%20needed%20to%20be%20fixed.%20They%20were%20supposed%20to%20last%2020%20years!%20I%20hate%20that%20I%20still%20can't%20bite%20into%20apples.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20wonders%20if%20this%20would%20be%20easier%20to%20fix%20if%20she'd%20had%20the%20option%20of%20no-preps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223fb15aae-5a2d-471d-94c9-937b445e50dc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatients%20are%20gravitating%20toward%20no-prep%20for%20their%20smile%20makeovers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20way%2C%20no-preps%20are%20like%20retro%20veneers%2C%20using%20the%20same%20feldspathic%20porcelain%20as%20they%20did%20in%20the%2080s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22No-prep%20veneers%20by%20Domino%20Dental%20in%20New%20York%20City%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f03429b8b41a9673fcb98f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENo-prep%20veneers%20by%20Domino%20Dental%20in%20New%20York%20City%3Cp%3EDomino%20Dental%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%3F%20A%20little%20more%20finesse%20because%20today's%20dentists%20have%20been%20doing%20veneers%20since%20they%20started%20and%20the%20practice%20come%20on%20leaps%20and%20bounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20deciding%20between%20the%20two%2C%20the%20first%20stage%20is%20to%20discuss%20your%20ultimate%20goals%20with%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdentist-and-orthodontist-debunk-15-common-teeth-myths-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edental%20professional%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20clear%20understanding%20of%20how%20you%20want%20to%20improve%20your%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20no-preps%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20original%20tooth%20remains%20entirely%20intact%2C%26quot%3B%20Marashi%20said.%20That%20means%20your%20teeth%20should%20be%20good%20for%20the%20long%20haul.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20decide%20to%20remove%20veneers%20later%20on%2C%20a%20laser%20can%20be%20used%20to%20remove%20the%20veneers%20and%20return%20the%20tooth%20to%20its%20original%20state.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20your%20dentist%20will%20determine%20whether%20no-prep%20veneers%20are%20an%20option%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20want%20to%20rethink%20no-prep%20if%20your%20goal%20is%20to%20significantly%20alter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-teeth-whitening-kit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20color%20of%20your%20teeth%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPatients%20with%20discolored%20front%20teeth%20that%20want%20a%20dramatic%20color%20change%20would%20also%20not%20be%20good%20candidate%20for%20this%20since%20no-prep%20veneers%20are%20very%20thin%2C%26quot%3B%20Horowitz%20said.%20%26quot%3BTraditional%20veneers%20are%20able%20to%20hide%20more%20imperfections%20in%20teeth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20if%20you%20have%20excessively%20crowded%20or%20large%20teeth%2C%20you%20will%20probably%20need%20a%20bit%20of%20drilling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deciding%20factor%20is%20how%20far%20out%20past%20the%20lip%20your%20teeth%20are.%20%26quot%3BUsually%2C%20if%20teeth%20are%20behind%20the%20wet%2Fdry%20border%20of%20your%20lower%20lip%2C%20there%20is%20some%20room%20to%20build%20out.%20Building%20teeth%20out%20past%20that%20border%20is%20not%20recommended%2C%26quot%3B%20Horowitz%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr.%20Lilya%20Horowitz%20at%20Domino%20Dental%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f034d8b8b41a9673fcb9b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223786%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDr.%20Lilya%20Horowitz%20at%20Domino%20Dental%20sees%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20want%20perfect%20teeth%20without%20all%20the%20drilling%3Cp%3EDomino%20Dental%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENo-prep%20does%20not%20necessarily%20mean%20a%20discounted%20price%20%E2%80%94%20some%20dental%20practices%20charge%20upwards%20of%20%243%2C500%20per%20tooth%20for%20no-preps%2C%20which%20is%20more%20than%20some%20charge%20for%20traditional%20veneers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20for%20this%20is%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20technique%2C%26quot%3B%20Horowitz%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20a%20lot%20more%20skills%20to%20remove%20very%20little%20or%20no%20tooth%20structure%20and%20create%20a%20beautiful%20result%20instead%20of%20drilling%20down%20the%20teeth%20and%20having%20a%20lot%20of%20room%20to%20work%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraditional%20veneers%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20can%20be%20faster%20because%20%26quot%3Bit%20does%20not%20require%20as%20much%20time%20to%20over-drill%20a%20tooth%20compared%20to%20a%20delicate%20and%20conservative%20tooth%20preparation%2C%26quot%3B%20Marashi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b58c6c34-d03e-4aa8-bd80-4837c7c44165%5C%22%3ETake%20care%20of%20your%20pearly%20whites!%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKeep%20in%20mind%20that%2C%20while%20veneers%20are%20made%20to%20last%2C%20the%20length%20of%20their%20lifespan%20fully%20depends%20on%20the%20skillset%20and%20execution%20of%20the%20dentist%20who%20applies%20them%20and%20post-treatment%20patient%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGeneral%20studies%20have%20shown%20a%2095%25%20survival%20rate%20of%20porcelain%20veneers%20over%20a%2010-year%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20Horowitz%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20well%20taken%20care%20of%20and%20bonded%20well%20to%20enamel%2C%20they%20can%20last%20multiple%20decades.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20long%20as%20your%20veneers%20are%20properly%20bonded%2C%20there%20should%20be%20no%20risk%20of%20plaque%20build-up%20or%20bacteria%20leakage%20beneath%20them%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20all%20veneers%20%E2%80%94%20like%20teeth%20%E2%80%94%20need%20TLC.%20That%20means%20brushing%2C%20flossing%2C%20and%20keeping%20up%20with%20regular%20cleanings%20as%20you%20always%20did%20with%20your%20teeth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fno-prep-veneers-new-trend-in-cosmetic-dentistry-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743846302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ed3e1a63d72727e198f041%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fno-prep-veneers-new-trend-in-cosmetic-dentistry-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22No-prep%20veneers%20are%20becoming%20the%20new%20%26quot%3Bit%26quot%3B%20cosmetic%20procedure.%20Demand%20for%20flawless%20teeth%20is%20still%20high.%20Shaving%20your%20teeth%20into%20spikes%3F%20Not%20so%20much.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Alexa%20Mellardo)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fno-prep-veneers-new-trend-in-cosmetic-dentistry-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Americans%20Are%20Rushing%20To%20Buy%20Essential%20Items%20Ahead%20Of%20Trump's%20Tariffs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20announced%20sweeping%20tariffs%20on%20foreign%20goods%2C%20Americans%20have%20just%20one%20thing%20on%20their%20minds%20-%20buy%20as%20much%20and%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%20to%20beat%20the%20price%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20prioritising%20essentials%20such%20as%20apparel%2C%20shoes%2C%20furniture%20and%20coffee%2C%20The%20Business%20Standard%20reported.%20And%20they%20are%20not%20leaving%20anything%20to%20chance.%20Many%2C%20who%20wanted%20to%20wait%20a%20while%2C%20have%20decided%20to%20buy%20automobiles%2C%20particularly%20those%20assembled%20outside%20the%20United%20States%2C%20to%20avoid%20paying%20steep%20prices%20when%20the%20tariffs%20kick%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EList%20of%20items%20Americans%20are%20stocking%20up%20on%20before%20the%20tariffs%20hit%20their%20wallets%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELaptops%20and%20smartphones%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Trump%20announced%20a%2032%20per%20cent%20tax%20on%20imports%20from%20Taiwan%20and%2052%20per%20cent%20on%20those%20from%20China%2C%20Americans%20rushed%20to%20buy%20tablets%2C%20smartphones%20and%20laptops.%20Their%20components%20are%20mostly%20sourced%20from%20abroad%2C%20especially%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EApparel%20and%20shoes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3