ot%20Honey%20from%20the%20counter%20at%20Paulie%20Gee's%2C%20gaining%20popularity%20by%20word%20of%20mouth.%20Eventually%2C%20he%20found%20a%20distributor%20and%20sold%20Mike's%20Hot%20Honey%20to%20its%20first%20retailer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.grubstreet.com%2F2014%2F09%2Fhot-honey.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhole%20Foods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20getting%20early%2C%20positive%20feedback%20was%20crucial%20to%20his%20success%20because%20it%20motivated%20him%20to%20continue.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20be%20afraid%20to%20just%20launch%20something%2C%20as%20new%20and%20rough%20around%20the%20edges%20as%20it%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Kurtz%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20gets%20a%20lot%20easier%20to%20make%20adjustments%20to%20an%20idea%20than%20trying%20to%20fine-tune%20something%20in%20your%20own%20echo%20chamber.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22464a23d3-579f-4cde-b4b6-3c4f9509b7f8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpend%20time%20with%20successful%20risk-takers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20Mike's%20Hot%20Honey%20bottles%20next%20to%20a%20pizza.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67effaa363d72727e199386f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224980%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMike's%20Hot%20Honey%20became%20a%20retail%20brand%20in%202014.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Aharoni%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2029%2C%20Kurtz's%20career%20in%20music%20was%20affected%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-warned-great-recession-2008-brooksley-born-wall-street-sexism-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2008%20recession%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20industry%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20in%20a%20healthy%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20he%20split%20his%20time%20between%20working%20at%20a%20booking%20agency%20and%20moonlighting%20as%20a%20pizza%20maker%20at%20Paulie%20Gee's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp