have%20to%20be%20perfect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20according%20to%20Evan%20King%20and%20Stefan%20Mai%2C%20cofounders%20of%20interview-prep%20startup%20Hello%20Interview.%20Previously%2C%20King%20worked%20as%20a%20staff%20engineer%20for%20Meta%2C%20while%20Mai%20has%20experience%20as%20an%20engineering%20manager%20at%20Amazon%20and%20a%20senior%20engineering%20manager%20at%20Meta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20little%20incentive%20to%20pass%20someone%20who%20doesn't%20get%20%3Cem%3Eeverything%3C%2Fem%3E%20entirely%20correct%2C%26quot%3B%20King%20and%20Mai%20wrote%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsletter.pragmaticengineer.com%2Fp%2Fthe-reality-of-tech-interviews%3Futm_campaign%3Demail-half-post%26r%3D1n9jf7%26utm_source%3Dsubstack%26utm_medium%3Demail%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Pragmatic%20Engineer%3C%2Fa%3E%20newsletter.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20grim%20reality%20of%20what%20happens%20when%20there%20are%20so%20many%20qualified%20candidates%20in%20the%20interview%20pool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20series%20of%20unfortunate%20circumstances%20have%20created%20the%20perfect%20storm%20for%20out-of-work%20engineers%2C%20they%20said.%20For%20one%2C%20there%20has%20only%20been%20about%20a%2040%25%20increase%20in%20the%20total%20number%20of%20jobs%20available%20since%20the%20market%20hit%20rock%20bottom%20in%202023%2C%20and%20companies%20are%20increasingly%20picky%20about%20who%20they%20onboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcomputer-science-major-panic-masters-degree-graduate-school-job-market-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20engineers%20of%20all%20experience%20levels%3C%2Fa%3E%20competing%20for%20a%20reduced%20number%20of%20roles%2C%20candidates%20are%20increasingly%20facing%20interviews%20that%20King%20and%20Mai%20said%20are%20only%20becoming%20harder%20to%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20core%20interview%20structure%20at%20Big%20Tech%20remains%20largely%20unchanged%2C%20the%20bar%20has%20shifted%20approximately%20one%20standard%20deviation%20higher%20across%20the%20board%2C%20and%20performance%20that%20would%20have%20secured%20an%20offer%20in%202021%20might%20not%20even%20clear%20the%20screening%20stage%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEngineers%20in%20niche%20specialties%20are%20doing%20better%2C%20King%20and%20Mai%20said%2C%20with%20the%20hiring%20market%20seeing%20an%20increased%20demand%20for%20those%20who%20have%20knowledge%20of%20%26quot%3BAI%20infrastructure%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmachine%20learning%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20among%20other%20things.%20Those%20in%20%26quot%3Bcore%20domains%2C%26quot%3B%20though%2C%20which%20the%20authors%20designate%20as%20frontend%2C%20backend%20services%2C%20and%20mobile%20development%2C%20are%20seeing%20fewer%20openings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20challenges%20aren't%20all%20equally%20punishing%2C%20though.%20King%20and%20Mai%20write%20that%20junior%20engineers%2C%20particularly%20those%20first%20entering%20the%20market%20after%20graduation%2C%20face%20the%20toughest%20field%20of%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20spoke%20to%20a%20job%20seeker%20who%20graduated%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institutes%20of%20Technology%20%E2%80%94%20which%20the%20authors%20describe%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20prestigious%20computer%20science%20university%20in%20the%20country%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20land%20a%20position%20for%206%20months%2C%20having%20applied%20to%20over%20100%20companies.%20The%20former%20student%20hasn't%20received%20a%20single%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompanies%20that%20once%20maintained%20robust%20university%20hiring%20programs%20have%20dramatically%20scaled%20them%20back%2C%20which%20is%20concerning%20because%20this%20could%20create%20an%20experience%20gap%20that%20impacts%20the%20industry%20for%20years%20to%20come%2C%20and%20could%20manifest%20in%20a%20'missing%20generation'%20of%20engineers%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20what%20junior%20programmers%20can%20do%20to%20increase%20their%20odds%2C%20King%20and%20Mai%20suggested%20shoring%20up%20on%20the%20fundamentals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20technical%20bar%20for%20junior%20roles%20has%20risen%20dramatically%2C%20making%20mastery%20of%20fundamental%20algorithms%20and%20data%20structures%20essential%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BSuccessful%20junior%20candidates%20typically%20solve%20150-200%20coding%20problems%20across%20all%20difficulty%20levels%20before%20interviewing.%20You%20must%20be%20a%20stronger%20coder%20before%20anything%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20competition%20is%20severe%2C%20it's%20not%20impossible%20to%20break%20through%2C%20said%20King%20and%20Mai.%20They%20wrote%20that%20though%20the%20interview%20process%20has%20essentially%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Bspecialized%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20candidates%20do%20have%20one%20advantage%20%E2%80%94%20the%20rules%20are%20public%2C%20and%20interviews%20can%20be%20practiced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20process%20might%20seem%20arbitrary%2C%20but%20with%20proper%20preparation%2C%20it's%20entirely%20learnable%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnyone%20with%20sufficient%20dedication%20can%20master%20these%20patterns%20and%20significantly%20improve%20their%20performance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20follow-up%20conversation%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Mai%20said%20the%20current%20job%20market%20heavily%20favors%20the%20prepared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20those%20who%20are%20able%20to%20put%20in%20the%20effort%2C%20and%20willing%20to%20put%20in%20the%20effort%2C%20I%20think%20the%20market%20is%20still%20one%20where%20you%20can%20find%20a%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20talk%20to%20too%20many%20people%2C%20you'll%20encounter%20a%20bunch%20of%20engineers%20who've%20been%20really%2C%20really%20struggling%2C%20but%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20peop