tory%20and%20targets%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amendment%20will%20reduce%20the%20religious%20and%20cultural%20autonomy%20of%20Muslims%2C%20said%20AAP%20MLA%20Amanatullah%20Khan%20in%20his%20plea%2C%20contending%20that%20the%20government's%20intervention%20undermines%20the%20rights%20of%20minorities%20to%20manage%20their%20religious%20and%20charitable%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20however%2C%20has%20maintained%20that%20the%20law%20will%20benefit%20Muslim%20women%20and%20ensure%20transparency%20in%20managing%20Waqf%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChallenging%20the%20constitutional%20validity%20of%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%20Mr%20Khan%20said%20the%20legislation%20violates%20multiple%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20citizens%2C%20including%20freedom%20of%20equality%2C%20managing%20religious%20affairs%2C%20and%20the%20rights%20of%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20curtails%20the%20religious%20and%20cultural%20autonomy%20of%20Muslims%2C%20enables%20arbitrary%20executive%20interference%2C%20and%20undermines%20the%20rights%20of%20minorities%20to%20manage%20their%20religious%20and%20charitable%20institutions%2C%20according%20to%20his%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20petition%20follows%20similar%20challenges%20by%20two%20opposition%20MPs%2C%20Congress's%20Mohammad%20Jawed%20and%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jawed%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20joint%20parliamentary%20committee%20on%20the%20Waqf%20bill%2C%20said%20the%20law%20discriminates%20against%20Muslims%20by%20imposing%20restrictions%20that%20are%20not%20present%20in%20the%20governance%20of%20other%20religious%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20major%20concerns%20against%20the%20law%20is%20a%20provision%20for%20including%20non-Muslim%20members%20in%20Waqf%20councils%20and%20state%20boards.%20This%20isn't%20the%20case%20with%20the%20Hindu%20Endowment%20Board%20or%20the%20Jain%20Endowment%20Board%20and%20is%20a%20grave%20violation%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20argued%20Mr%20Owaisi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20%26quot%3Busing%20its%20majority%20in%20parliament%20not%20to%20reform%2C%20but%20to%20destroy%2C%20to%20take%20away%20all%20the%20rights%20Muslims%20have%3B%20you%20are%20by%20enacting%20a%20law%20waging%20a%20war%20on%20Muslims%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-government-using-parliament-majority-to-take-away-muslims-rights-asaduddin-owaisi-to-ndtv-8088564%5C%22%3EOwaisi%20said%20while%20speaking%20to%20NDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefending%20the%20bill%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Prasad%20told%20NDTV%20it%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-bjp-no-mosques-will-be-touched-bjps-ravi-shankar-prasad-on-waqf-bill-8089460%5C%22%3Ebring%20transparency%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20making%20Waqf%20boards%20accountable.%20Seeking%20to%20allay%20fears%20that%20the%20law%20would%20take%20away%20Waqf%20properties%2C%20he%20insisted%20that%20no%20mosque%20or%20graveyard%20is%20going%20to%20be%20touched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-clears-lok-sabha-with-288-votes-in-favour-232-against-after-heated-debate-8073068%5C%22%3ELok%20Sabha%20cleared%20the%20Waqf%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E%20early%20Thursday%20by%20288%20votes%20to%20232%20after%20a%20heated%20face-off%20between%20the%20opposition%20and%20treasury%20benches%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20with%20128%20votes%20in%20favour%20and%2095%20against.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill's%20passage%20sparked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-bill-protests-kolkata-ahmedabad-chennai-waqf-amendment-bill-clears-parliament-8086039%5C%22%3Emassive%20protests%20in%20various%20citie%3C%2Fa%3Es%20like%20Kolkata%2C%20Chennai%2C%20and%20Ahmedabad%20after%20Friday's%20weekly%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22p