3Cli%3EInker%20advises%20investing%20in%20non-US%20stocks%20due%20to%20valuation%20discounts%20and%20economic%20risks%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-raising-prices-increases-trump-tariffs-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Trump's%20tariff%20rollout%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20sank%20the%20one%20justification%20investors%20had%20for%20buying%20into%20an%20already%20expensive%20US%20stock%20market%2C%20according%20to%20Jeremy%20Grantham's%20right-hand%20man%2C%20Ben%20Inker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20best%20bull%20case%20one%20could%20have%20had%20for%20it%20was%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20relative%20to%20other%20stock%20indices%20around%20the%20world%2C%20yes%20it's%20a%20lot%20more%20expensive%2C%20but%20US%20companies%20are%20the%20envy%20of%20the%20world%20and%20they%20make%20a%20lot%20more%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20co-head%20of%20asset%20allocation%20and%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20GMO%20told%20BI%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20with%20what%20just%20happened%20is%20I%20think%20this%20kind%20of%20blows%20a%20whole%20in%20that%20'yes%2C%20but%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%20tariffs%20will%20hurt%20the%20ability%20of%20large-cap%20growth%20firms%20%E2%80%94%20which%20have%20driven%20much%20of%20the%20market's%20performance%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20%E2%80%94%20to%20keep%20their%20profit%20margins%20high%2C%20Inker%20said.%20He%20cited%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-trump-tariffs-china-liberation-day-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20an%20example.%20The%20company's%20share%20price%20has%20fallen%20almost%2016%25%20since%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20Apple's%20stock%20went%20down%20as%20much%20as%20it%20did%20was%20because%20tariffs%20are%20going%20to%20really%20raise%20the%20price%20of%20production%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BApple%20has%20wonderful%20margins%2C%20but%20that%20means%20when%20the%20cost%20of%20production%20goes%20up%2C%20some%20of%20that%20eats%20into%20their%20margin%2C%20so%20they%20get%20lower%20sales%20and%20lower%20margins.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20this%20week's%20sizable%20market%20rout%2C%20Inker%20said%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20remains%20overvalued%20by%2030%25%20to%2040%25.%20Since%20early%202022%2C%20GMO's%20cofounder%20Jeremy%20Grantham%20has%20regularly%20warned%20that%20stocks%20are%20in%20a%20bubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20the%20sell-off%20would%20continue%2C%20Inker%20said%20it's%20possible%20given%20the%20current%20valuation%20premium%20and%20protectionist%20policy%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it%20wants%20to%20fall%20to%20fair%20value%2C%20it's%20got%20plenty%20of%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20Inker%20said%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20what%20I%20would%20have%20recommended%20the%20government%20do%20if%20it%20wanted%20to%20keep%20the%20stock%20market%20up.%20The%20best%20way%20to%20keep%20an%20expensive%20stock%20market%20up%20is%20to%20help%20companies%20continue%20to%20look%20exceptional%2C%20and%20this%20ain't%20the%20way%20to%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInker%20said%20his%20positioning%20hasn't%20changed%20much%20in%20recent%20days%2C%20and%20that%20he%20still%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20preference%26quot%3B%20for%20non-US%20stocks%20compared%20to%20US%20stocks%20because%20of%20the%20valuation%20discount%20that%20exists%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20tariffs%20don't%20bode%20well%20for%20the%20US%20economy%2C%20he%20said.%20Wall%20Street%20agrees%3A%20JPMorgan%20now%20says%20there's%20a%2060%25%20chance%20of%20a%20recession%20in%202025%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20places%20those%20odds%20at%2035%25%2C%20and%20UBS%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20a%20downturn%20is%20likely%20if%20tariffs%20are%20not%20reduced%20in%20the%20months%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20this%20sticks%20around%2C%20this%20will%20be%20sort%20of%20a%20disaster%20for%20aggregate%20productivity%20and%20GDP%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20Inker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20to%20gain%20exposure%20to%20non-US%20stocks%20is%20through%20funds%20like%20the%20Vanguard%20FTSE%20All%20World%20ex%20US%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fvanguard-ftse-all-world-ex-us-index-fund-etf-shares-us9220427754%3FmiRedirects%3D2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVEU%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20the%20iShares%20MSCI%20ACWI%20ex%20US%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fishares-msci-acwi-ex-us-etf-us4642882405%3FmiRedirects%3D2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EACWX%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20quarterly%20letter%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Inker%20also%20urged%20investors%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20US%20high-yield%20credit%20given%20the%20economic%20uncertainty.%20The%20assets%20are%20considered%20higher-risk%20because%20the%20companies%20issuing%20the%20bonds%20have%20less%20solid%20fundamentals%20and%20therefore%20an%20increased%20likelihood%20of%20going%20under%20and%20defaulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-sp500-overvalued-tariffs-trade-war-inker-gmo-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743843601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f0436263d72727e1994954%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-sp500-overvalued-tariffs-trade-war-inker-gmo-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20best%20way%20to%20keep%20an%20expensive%20stock%20market%20up%20is%20to%20help%20companies%20continue%20to%20look%20exceptional%2C%20and%20this%20ain't%20the%20way%20t