r%20budget%2C%20prioritizing%20building%20your%20emergency%20fund%2C%20or%20strategically%20acquiring%20undervalued%20assets%20when%20opportunities%20arise%2C%26quot%3B%20Tolani%20Eweje%2C%20who%20writes%20the%20Substack%20newsletter%20The%20Creator%20Success%20Club%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20other%20creators%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221e79bc1e-9f53-4c93-9752-16ec2b17f89f%5C%22%3E'Stay%20the%20course'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETori%20Dunlap%2C%20the%20creator%20of%20Her%20First%20%24100K%20with%202.2%20million%20followers%20on%20Instagram%2C%20encouraged%20people%20to%20avoid%20%26quot%3Bpanic-selling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20No.%201%20financial%20tip%20right%20now%20is%20to%20stay%20the%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20stock%20market%20is%20like%20a%20roller%20coaster%20%E2%80%94%20there%20will%20always%20be%20ups%20and%20downs%2C%20but%20the%20people%20who%20build%20real%20wealth%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20stay%20strapped%20in%20for%20the%20long%20haul.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBola%20Sokunbi%2C%20the%20creator%20of%20Clever%20Girl%20Finance%20with%20356%2C000%20followers%20on%20Instagram%2C%20also%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20panic.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20to%20focus%20on%20long-term%20financial%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMallory%20Rowan%2C%20a%20finance%20influencer%20with%20108%2C000%20followers%20and%20host%20of%20the%20YouTube%20show%20%26quot%3BThe%20Inbetweeners%26quot%3B%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BReflect%20on%20what%20it%20is%20you%20need%20to%20feel%20good%20about%20your%20money%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20global%20climate%2C%20and%20what%20that%20tangibly%20looks%20like.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERowan%20said%20that%20check-in%20can%20look%20like%20regular%20money%20chats%20with%20your%20partner%20or%20making%20changes%20to%20feel%20like%20you%20have%20forward%20movement%20in%20your%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c508fc54-00fa-4748-8168-cb248dacfde2%5C%22%3E'No%20level%20of%20income%20is%20above%20budgeting'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMal%20Baska%2C%20who%20has%2030%2C00%20followers%20on%20Instagram%20for%20her%20Money%20Talk%20Mal%20account%2C%20said%20to%20get%20your%20budget%20in%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20level%20of%20income%20is%20above%20budgeting%20to%20some%20degree%2C%26quot%3B%20Baska%20said.%20%26quot%3BHaving%20a%20pulse%20and%20a%20plan%20for%20your%20incoming%20cash%20flow%20is%20key%20to%20financial%20security%20all%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20but%20especially%20during%20times%20of%20uncertainty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENadia%20Vanderhall%2C%20a%20financial%20planner%20with%208%2C000%20followers%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20said%20to%20look%20at%20your%20last%20month%20of%20spending%20and%20see%20what%20expenses%20have%20gone%20up%2C%20like%20groceries%20or%20gas.%20Use%20that%20to%20shape%20your%20budget%20for%20the%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaska%20also%20said%20now%20is%20the%20time%20to%20negotiate%20your%20salary%20and%20costs%2C%20such%20as%20auto%20insurance%2C%20cellphone%2C%20and%20medical%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLock%20in%20pricing%20before%20companies%20really%20get%20hit%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20can%20help%20free%20up%20cash%20flow%20in%20the%20budget.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226aa693dd-b989-431a-9896-e4fb40e3f1dc%5C%22%3E'Prioritize%20creating%20a%20cash%20buffer'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20the%20time%20to%20bulk%20up%20your%20emergency%20fund%2C%20a%20few%20of%20the%20influencers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20No.%201%20piece%20of%20advice%20I'm%20giving%20people%20is%20really%20to%20prioritize%20creating%20a%20cash%20buffer%2C%26quot%3B%20Sokunbi%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20an%20income%20coming%20in%20right%20now%2C%20this%20is%20the%20time%20to%20be%20saving%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaska%20recommended%20opening%20a%20high-yield%20savings%20account%20and%20budgeting%20to%20grow%20that%20safety%20net%20if%20you%20haven't%20already.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22936d423d-7db0-42bf-a810-cc69722f3c9e%5C%22%3E'Turn%20today's%20dip%20into%20long-term%20gains'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20silver%20lining%20to%20a%20market%20downturn%20is%20the%20opportunity%20to%20buy%20quality%20stocks%20and%20index%20funds%20at%20a%20discount%2C%20said%20Kelly%20Anne%20Smith%2C%20the%20creator%20of%20Freedom%20In%20A%20Budget%2C%20which%20has%2053%2C000%20subscribers%20on%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20market%20has%20a%20history%20of%20recovering%20over%20time%2C%20and%20that%20rebound%20could%20turn%20today's%20dip%20into%20long-term%20gains%20for%20your%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESokunbi%20also%20said%20this%20could%20be%20a%20good%20time%20to%20invest%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20don't%20need%20the%20money%20within%20the%20next%20five%20years%20and%20already%20have%20your%20cash%20buffer%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20retirement%20is%20not%20anywhere%20around%20the%20corner%2C%20this%20is%20the%20stock%20market%20on%20sale%2C%20and%20we%20love%20a%20great%20sale%2C%26quot%3B%20Sokunbi%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20take%20advantage%20of%20it%2C%20keeping%20in%20mind%20that%20you%20want%20to%20have%20a%20cash%20buffer%20in%20place%20so%20that%20if%20you%20do%20need%20the%20money%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20cash%20out%20your%20investments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f7802aad-cc17-497e-90af-03a6e992d850%5C%22%3ETravel%20where%20the%20exchange%20rate%20is%20strong%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERising%20prices%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-dollar-is-down-dxy-trump-tariff-trade-war-economy-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweak%20dollar%3C%2Fa%3E%20don't%20have%20to%20ruin%20your%20travel%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGo%20somewhere%20where%20the%20exchange%20rate%20is%20strong%20and%20in%20favor%20of%20your%20home%20currency%2C%26quot%3B%20Vivian%20Tu%2C%20the%