20as%20president%20too%2C%20but%20since%20his%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House%20he%20has%20appeared%20more%20unbowed%20than%20ever%20in%20the%20face%20of%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELess%20than%2024%20hours%20after%20his%20world-shaking%20tariff%20announcement%2C%20and%20as%20markets%20were%20still%20plunging%20into%20the%20red%2C%20Trump%20headed%20to%20Florida%20for%20dinner%20on%20Thursday%20at%20Trump%20National%20Doral%20golf%20club.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20club%20is%20hosting%20an%20event%20this%20weekend%20by%20the%20Saudi-owned%20LIV%20Golf%20tour%2C%20for%20which%20Trump%20is%20trying%20to%20broker%20a%20merger%20with%20the%20PGA%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelevision%20footage%20showed%20Trump%2C%20wearing%20a%20read%20%26quot%3BMake%20America%20Great%20Again%26quot%3B%20hat%2C%20being%20driven%20in%20a%20golf%20cart%20after%20arriving%20on%20his%20Marine%20One%20helicopter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20a%20disgrace%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Republicans%20Against%20Trump%20group%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20sharing%20the%20footage%2C%20noting%20that%20it%20came%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20market%20is%20crashing%2C%20a%20recession%20is%20looming%2C%20and%20the%20country%20is%20more%20isolated%20than%20ever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%20morning%20Trump%20then%20headed%20to%20another%20of%20his%20golf%20courses%20near%20his%20grand%20Mar-a-Lago%20residence%20in%20Palm%20Beach%2C%20just%20as%20US%20markets%20were%20opening%20for%20a%20second%20day's%20bloodbath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20great%20time%20to%20get%20rich%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%20shortly%20before%20heading%20to%20the%20course%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bmy%20policies%20will%20never%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Fired'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocrats%20criticized%20Trump%20for%20missing%20the%20return%20ceremony%20on%20Friday%20for%20four%20US%20troops%20killed%20during%20a