%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246267%2Fmenstrual-hygiene-kit-cloth-pads-avni-safepads-women-health-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20health%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecame%20while%20developing%20training%20materials%20for%20non-literate%20communities.%20She%20realised%20the%20visuals%20she%20was%20drawing%20didn%E2%80%99t%20resonate%20with%20people.%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20to%20school%20have%20a%20completely%20different%20way%20of%20drawing.%20So%2C%20I%20created%20a%20picture%20dictionary%20on%20how%20menstruation%2C%20abortion%2C%20and%20delivery%20should%20be%20depicted.%20That%20became%20the%20basis%20for%20our%20training%20manuals%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-4175