%2FTBI-featured-image-4_11zon-1743598578-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-4_11zon-1743598578-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-417540%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELakshmi%20leads%20a%20UNICEF-backed%20session%20where%20boys%20explored%20menstruation%2C%20cooking%2C%20and%20gender%20roles%20to%20challenge%20deep-rooted%20stereotypes.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20helped%20design%20the%20UNICEF-backed%20%E2%80%98Positive%20Masculinity%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20where%20boys%20learned%20about%20menstruation%2C%20cooked%20meals%2C%20and%20invited%20family%20members%20to%20break%20gender%20stereotypes.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20boys%20to%20understand%20the%20changes%20in%20the%20female%20body.%20It%20was%20very%20powerful%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStarting%20a%20PhD%20at%2050%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%2050s%2C%20Lakshmi%20received%20an%20unexpected%20opportunity%20%E2%80%94%20an%20official%20letter%20from%20NID%20equating%20her%20diploma%20to%20a%20post-graduate%20degree%2C%20making%20her%20eligible%20for%20a%20PhD.%20She%20enrolled%20at%20IIT%20Bombay%20and%20completed%20her%20thesis%20over%20eight%20years%2C%20even%20as%20she%20navigated%20personal%20loss%20and%20family%20responsibilities.%20%E2%80%9CI%20lost%20my%20husband.%20My%20daughter%20got%20married%20and%20had%20a%20child.%20I%20had%20to%20help%20her.%20But%20I%20kept%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20PhD%20focused%20on%20the%20sustainability%20of%20menstrual%20management%2C%20applying%20what%20she%20calls%20the%20PASS%20model%20%E2%80%94%20Paryavaran%20(Environment)%2C%20Arthik%20(Economics)%2C%20Swasthya%20(Health)%2C%20and%20Samaj%20(Society)%20%E2%80%94%20to%20assess%20menstrual%20products%20holistically.%20%E2%8